{"tid":1774811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁care人數既，唔該下次跟足規矩維園出發","createTime":"2019-12-08T13:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T14:21:16.000Z","uid":68080,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4542b5eb4c905cb751e64e6c479d9023f4e7077d","tid":1774811,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"又要怕辛苦又嫌少<br />\n有無考慮過你企出黎但係唔過D checkpoint就唔計<br />\n<br />\n有心既就下次遊行好好睇睇維園出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見住D爸爸媽媽銀髮族守規矩企係到等你打完尖先行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話你有老有嫩打尖都算數 又唔係話明知會塞點解要維園<br />\n變相懲罰守規矩既人<br />\n<br />\n另外岑子杰都話80萬人係難統計同埋想大家早D散。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]你一開始跟規矩維園出，數到人頭，但係後面黑警搞事行唔到都係有過百萬人出黎<br />\n而家亂插入黎你行左都唔知<br />\n<br />\n所以今日檢討完之後，唔該大家維園出［/red]</span>"},{"pid":"d571b50f17e8b8267353be8daae8d0733e387850","tid":1774811,"uid":63157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"究竟係為人數已行,定係為訴求而行"},{"pid":"cf243d0cb690c8c589b747c91e7ddf74607c3b06","tid":1774811,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔好傻啦 不嬲鵝頸橋 金鐘橋都有數人數"},{"pid":"03867a3dd93707438d952d3caf45bce60266f00c","tid":1774811,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d571b50f17e8b8267353be8daae8d0733e387850","tid":1774811,"uid":63157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"究竟係為人數已行,定係為訴求而行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"為訴求<br />\n但係人數有班人好care 覺得係衡量民意既重點"},{"pid":"1de0b6b9960e25f81eb75db18d6773cb16e9d4e1","tid":1774811,"uid":268246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"推，唔好再因為人數嘈，檢討再做好"},{"pid":"4fbafefa4cc63b44dd3cf26ea8041103fa2607c3","tid":1774811,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf243d0cb690c8c589b747c91e7ddf74607c3b06","tid":1774811,"uid